            "answer_text": "Yes and no. Yes, or I mean YES! Because what kind of gamer am I to not love this amazing game? Cybernetic humanity in a gritty world and interesting story? Check. Smooth, logically introduced Diegetic Interface? Check. Smooth and stylish gunplay yet tactical at the same time? Check. Uniquely designed characters and artstyle? Check. Multiple play path that rewards players\u2019 agency? Check Let\u2019s just say there are a lot to love and a lot to get hyped for. But that is why I am trying not to look forward to the game, because damn, I would get so involved with it, would love it so much, that by the time I finished it, I would have an empty hole in my soul. I have to temper my expectation. ",
